to say anything
about other people

16:31.990 --> 16:33.490
When they're not around.

16:33.491 --> 16:36.493
Especially
if a camera is rolling.

16:39.330 --> 16:40.464
Gotcha, dad.

16:40.465 --> 16:42.800
